'From Squeak3.7beta of ''1 April 2004'' [latest update: #5967] on 17 September 2004 at 12:44:35 am'!"Change Set:		DictionaryEnhDate:			17 September 2004Author:			Alexandre BergelAdd an includesAssociation: method to test if an association is contained in a dictionary"!!Dictionary methodsFor: 'testing' stamp: 'ab 9/17/2004 00:39'!includesAssociation: anAssociation  ^ (self         associationAt: anAssociation key      ifAbsent: [ ^ false ]) value = anAssociation value! !